/2d-gaussian-splatting/
unreal/runtime/Plugins/*/Binaries/
unreal/runtime/Plugins/*/Intermediate/
unreal/runtime/Plugins/*/_ref/

*.safetensors
*.ckpt
*.gguf
*.pth
*.bin
*.onnx

